ATTRIBUTION FOR UPSTREAM SOURCES

This dataset compiles values from the following sources. Please cite them in
addition to the present dataset whenever you redistribute or build upon it.

  1. Pérez-Francisco, J. M. et al. (2024). "Rigid alicyclic polyimide films
     based on BTD dianhydride." Polymers, 16(22), 3188.
     DOI: 10.3390/polym16223188. License: CC-BY-3.0.

  2. Ren, X. et al. (2023). "Fluorene-containing dianhydride polyimides with
     amide-bridged diamines." Polymers, 15(17), 3549.
     DOI: 10.3390/polym15173549. License: CC-BY-4.0.

  3. Lecoeur, S. et al. (2024). "DOPO-functionalized poly(2,6-dimethyl-1,
     4-phenylene oxide) oligomers." Polymers, 16(2), 303.
     DOI: 10.3390/polym16020303. License: CC-BY-4.0.

  4. LamaLab. Polymer Tg dataset on Zenodo.
     DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.15783761. License as declared on the Zenodo record.

  5. PubChem (NIH/NLM). Compound records resolved via PUG-REST for monomer
     identification. Public domain.
